					<div id="heading">
						<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
											</div>

					<p>No personal identifiable information is collected by Weather.com.au Pty Ltd.
	The web server does however log low level information for each request for
	statistical purposes only. Information logged for each request includes -</p>
<ul>
	<li>Your IP address</li>
	<li>Date and time </li>
	<li>Page visited</li>
	<li>Referring web page</li>
	<li>Your Web Browser</li>
</ul>
<p>We will not make an attempt to identify users or their browsing activities.
	However, in the unlikely event of an investigation, a law enforcement agency
	or other government agency may exercise its legal authority to inspect our web
	server logs.</p>
<p>We will only record your e-mail address if you send us a message. Your e-mail
	address will only be used or disclosed for the purpose for which you have provided
	it and it will not be added to a mailing list or used or disclosed for any other
	purpose without your consent.</p>
<p>Weather.com.au does not utilise browser cookies. However, third party sites
	such as our advertising partners may set cookies for the purpose of serving
	ads.</p>
<p>For further information regarding our privacy policy, please use the <a href="/about/contact">contact
		form</a>.</p>

